<item>
            <title>[JOHNZON-49] ciruclar exceptions ends in StackOverflowException in JAXRS provider</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JOHNZON-49</link>
                <project id="12315523" key="JOHNZON">Johnzon</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It is ok to fil for circular objects when the user can handle it but it is not the case for exception&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Solution: removing cause and suppressedException seems acceptable. If you really want it just customize the mapper (through the builder as usual) overriding this config:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;builder.setIgnoreFieldsForType(Throwable.class);
&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// or to still ignore suppressedException
&lt;/span&gt;builder.setIgnoreFieldsForType(Throwable.class, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;suppressedException&quot;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
